      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRAVADO (2) was below best at his last start when 8th at this track following a third place finish (19.48) there two back. Solid record here at the distance winning 10 races. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can make amends. SAILPLANE (3) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing third and beaten a neck (19.79) behind One Knee Noni at this track. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to be in the finish again. HAPPY BUDDHA (7) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at Shepparton in a handy 22.58 beating Morning Daisy. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Shapes as a top winning chance on latest effort. TROPIC MAN (4) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
